    "hazard": "river_flood | tsunami | landslide | storm_surge | inland_flood",
    "ksj_urls": "List of MLIT KSJ download URLs (zip of Shapefile or GML). Resolver unions polygons across all URLs. One URL is fine; multiple is for sources that span multiple regional / prefectural KSJ files.",
