    "notes": "(optional) free-text — e.g. 'national-managed; under Kanto regional bureau A31-21_83'."
  },
  "_ksj_file_naming": "A31 (river flood) files are organised by regional bureau OR prefecture. 81=Hokkaido, 82=Tohoku, 83=Kanto, 84=Hokuriku, 85=Chubu, 86=Kinki, 87=Chugoku, 88=Shikoku, 89=Kyushu (national-managed rivers). 01-47 = JIS prefecture codes (prefecture-managed rivers). A given PLATEAU source-document may span both — list both URLs.",
